{"x": 0.8925, "y": 0.1349}, {"x": 0.8925, "y": 0.2529}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.2529}], "comment": "The introduction outlines general factors but does not frame a clear knowledge question. Explicitly link this paragraph to the IA prompt by posing a focused TOK question to guide your exploration of justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "7e1c512c-4fd0-47f0-9bdd-d2445be25ba1", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.134, "y": 0.0868, "width": 0.7346, "height": 0.024099999999999996}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.134, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.8686, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.8686, "y": 0.1109}, {"x": 0.134, "y": 0.1109}], "comment": "The title restates the IA code but lacks engagement. Recast it as an inquiry-based knowledge question to immediately capture the TOK focus on justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "bbf89e29-0cef-47cc-9fb1-be7cd96846c4", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.3629, "width": 0.3761, "height": 0.020899999999999974}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.3629}, {"x": 0.4899, "y": 0.3629}, {"x": 0.4899, "y": 0.3838}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.3838}], "comment": "The object header names the album but omits its release date and cultural impact. Including these specifics would situate the object in its real-world context more precisely.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "244f30af-b3e7-40cd-8b04-7060cb370599", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.3057, "y": 0.4297, "width": 0.37789999999999996, "height": 0.26799999999999996}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.3057, "y": 0.4297}, {"x": 0.6836, "y": 0.4297}, {"x": 0.6836, "y": 0.6977}, {"x": 0.3057, "y": 0.6977}], "comment": "The image description focuses on visual detail but doesn\u00e2\u0080\u0099t link the cover\u00e2\u0080\u0099s symbolism to the TOK concepts you discuss. Draw connections between the artwork and your ideas about justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "90c7b3bc-e94f-46ec-942f-bde07db53fcf", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.7359}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8526}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8526}], "comment": "The claim \u00e2\u0080\u009cUTOPIA is the greatest rap album of 2024\u00e2\u0080\u009d lacks defined criteria. Clarify what makes an album \u00e2\u0080\u0098great\u00e2\u0080\u0099 (e.g., innovation, influence) before applying tests of truth to justify it.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f04a83dd-a3eb-4ea0-9256-389cc7f019d0", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.7359}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8526}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8526}], "comment": "Relying on personal emotional reaction offers anecdotal support but weak TOK analysis. Integrate the pragmatic test by explaining how usefulness or practical effects justify belief in the album\u00e2\u0080\u0099s quality.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "ea2b4d4a-9f15-42df-82fb-c27521acce1b", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1857, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.44210000000000005}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1857}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1857}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.6278}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.6278}], "comment": "Your logical critique correctly identifies the disconnect in Trump\u00e2\u0080\u0099s argument. To deepen this, apply the coherence test by examining whether the tweet\u00e2\u0080\u0099s premises support its conclusion consistently.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "2aa3c185-65ff-4ef8-8fb9-c90e0a3c0aca", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.3566, "y": 0.4466, "width": 0.27740000000000004, "height": 0.349}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.3566, "y": 0.4466}, {"x": 0.634, "y": 0.4466}, {"x": 0.634, "y": 0.7956}, {"x": 0.3566, "y": 0.7956}], "comment": "The image shows the phone physically but not the authentication process. Consider including a screenshot of the Face ID in action to better illustrate the TOK issue of evidence versus interpretation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "9f42e18d-f8c4-47d4-a33a-0504eac22004", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.7359}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8526}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8526}], "comment": "The term \u00e2\u0080\u009ctruthness\u00e2\u0080\u009d is non-standard in TOK. Use the term \u00e2\u0080\u009ctruth\u00e2\u0080\u009d and provide a precise definition, then differentiate it from related concepts like justification and belief.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d3a0fbd5-370d-44d2-913a-bcf54ea31fbc", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1518, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.2471}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1518}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1518}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.3989}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.3989}], "comment": "Claiming Face ID as the \u00e2\u0080\u0098best\u00e2\u0080\u0099 verification procedure is subjective. Define explicit criteria (accuracy, speed, security) and link these to TOK concepts of sufficiency and reliability of evidence.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f48fe23c-8c81-45cc-894e-bf5306c35f4f", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.4448, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.41090000000000004}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.4448}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.4448}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8557}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8557}], "comment": "The exploration of a counterclaim adds depth. To enhance this, incorporate real-world hack statistics or documented Face ID failures as evidence to ground your TOK analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "a670ed16-c181-4f5f-bc43-b21330aa15b7", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.4448, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.41090000000000004}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.4448}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.4448}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8557}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8557}], "comment": "Your discussion of subjectivity is promising. Strengthen it by explicitly connecting to the TOK distinction between personal and shared knowledge and how this affects justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "ac9a2e89-0da2-4763-bb1e-397bade7064c", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.6407, "width": 0.3415, "height": 0.022299999999999986}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.6407}, {"x": 0.456, "y": 0.6407}, {"x": 0.456, "y": 0.663}, {"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.663}], "comment": "The header notes the tweet but omits the date and platform context here. Reiterate its publication details to firmly situate this object in its real-world setting.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "0b3d4537-f324-4d9a-8bc3-b8c85d60c4d9", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.7359}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8526}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8526}], "comment": "The statistic of \u00e2\u0080\u009c3 billion streams\u00e2\u0080\u009d needs a clear source citation and analysis of what consensus it demonstrates. Evaluate whether popularity equates to justified truth in your claim.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "da8e38e1-c2cb-43f3-8724-85c405d47641", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.3798, "width": 0.444, "height": 0.023099999999999954}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.3798}, {"x": 0.5585, "y": 0.3798}, {"x": 0.5585, "y": 0.4029}, {"x": 0.1145, "y": 0.4029}], "comment": "Labeling the object as \u00e2\u0080\u009cFace Identification\u00e2\u0080\u009d is vague. Specify it as \u00e2\u0080\u009cFace ID technology\u00e2\u0080\u009d and note the model\u00e2\u0080\u0099s release year to anchor the object in a clear real-world context.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "3874b6b1-d506-4332-bf0d-861a9557fbe7", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.2214, "y": 0.7137, "width": 0.5571999999999999, "height": 0.138}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.2214, "y": 0.7137}, {"x": 0.7786, "y": 0.7137}, {"x": 0.7786, "y": 0.8517}, {"x": 0.2214, "y": 0.8517}], "comment": "You present the tweet\u00e2\u0080\u0099s metrics but do not analyze their impact. Discuss how retweets and likes can influence perceived credibility, linking to TOK notions of authority and consensus.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "442c8911-a488-4013-b14e-b27fd97bd3ad", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.675, "width": 0.7761, "height": 0.0837}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.675}, {"x": 0.8899, "y": 0.675}, {"x": 0.8899, "y": 0.7587}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.7587}], "comment": "The conclusion restates factors affecting justification but is too general. Synthesize insights from all three objects to form a cohesive answer to the core knowledge question.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "bca14c26-e45f-4962-a450-7ce3946c2fec", "versionId": "6072fb78-e672-4e8b-963b-f13b48861559", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167, "width": 0.7767999999999999, "height": 0.7359}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.1167}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.8526}, {"x": 0.1138, "y": 0.8526}], "comment": "Incorporating both the correspondence and consensus tests demonstrates awareness of multiple truth criteria; continue by explicitly comparing their strengths and limitations in your example.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "ccaae5ff-e8ef-4594-acb5-285655747726", "title": "What counts as good evidence for a claim?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-A", "tok", "sl", "reverse-graded"], "slug": "what-counts-as-good-evidence-for-a-claim-